Screening of Multiple Biomarkers Associated With Ischemic Stroke in Atrial 
Fibrillation.

Hijazi Z(1)(2), Wallentin L(1)(2), Lindbäck J(2), Alexander JH(3), Connolly 
SJ(4), Eikelboom JW(4), Ezekowitz MD(5)(6), Granger CB(3), Lopes RD(3), Pol 
