Outpatient uterine assessment and treatment unit in patients with abnormal 
uterine bleeding: an economic modelling study.

Bennett A(1), Thavorn K(2), Arendas K(1), Coyle D(1), Singh SS(1).

Author information:
(1)Clinical Epidemiology Program (Bennett, Thavorn), Ottawa Hospital Research 
Institute; School of Epidemiology and Public Health (Bennett, Thavorn, Arendas, 
Coyle, Singh), University of Ottawa; ICES uOttawa (Thavorn); Department of 
